description:
The Losers head into the caves to find El Cuco. As they collect rocks and stones, they offer their final thoughts on the first season of HBO's The Outsider. Bonus: They also offer a Coronavirus update with plenty of Stand bits. Special guest includes Jenn Adams from The Horror Virgin podcast.
